{"tid":1135683,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［童年回憶］想搵翻一集小丸子","createTime":"2019-05-02T12:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T15:11:13.000Z","uid":188377,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d4382f25702f96170bc4024ae17ede23524e4047","tid":1135683,"uid":188377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T12:46:03.000Z","msg":"個集故事係講小丸子放長假最後一日先趕功課<br />\n做唔切要成家幫手 <br />\n但夜啲個個都走哂去瞓覺 得番小丸子繼續做<br />\n其中有樣功課係畫幅畫<br />\n小丸子結果求其塗黑成張畫紙 話係「停電的晚上」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個睇過 應該係漫畫 搵左好耐都搵唔翻<br />\n希望有80/90後巴絲打幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感謝"},{"pid":"6182c7f0c9a65b1827110b801b5ee4a5b7ac1173","tid":1135683,"uid":204659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"擬似內容的一集<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x5i_59JlQqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx5i_59JlQqM&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=4625ce75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x5i_59JlQqM</a><br />\n<br />\n反而另外想找一集<br />\n講小丸子同埋幾個同學去左花輪屋企睇攝影機播片<br />\n講花輪雖然好有錢<br />\n其實背後都付出左好多努力去學習如何做一個紳士"}]}